8 Section 427.16. A. There is hereby created a medical marijuana
9 transporter license as a category of the medical marijuana business
10 license.
11 B. Pursuant to Section 424 of this title, the Oklahoma Medical
12 Marijuana Authority shall issue a medical marijuana transporter
13 license to licensed medical marijuana commercial growers, processors
14 and dispensaries upon issuance of such licenses and upon each
15 renewal. Medical marijuana transporter licenses shall also be
16 issued to licensed medical marijuana research facilities, medical
17 marijuana education facilities and medical marijuana testing
18 laboratories upon issuance of such licenses and upon each renewal.
19 C. A medical marijuana transporter license may also be issued
20 to qualifying applicants who are registered with the Secretary of
21 State and otherwise meet the requirements for a medical marijuana
22 business license set forth in the Oklahoma Medical Marijuana and
23 Patient Protection Act and the requirements set forth in this
24 section to provide logistics, distribution and storage of medical
HB2807 HFLR Page 2
